How to run:

1.Open testng.xml file
2.Right click on it and run -> TESTNG suite


Approaches:
 
1.Created base file with the driver initiation and close methods.
2.Created two page object classes in the "com.pageObject" package,which contains all the locators and action methods.
3.Created two test classes for two scenarios in the "com.testcases" package.
4.created utilities to add the listeners with the failed scenario which will get the screenshot on test failure,
  with the test method name as a file name and store into the"screenshot" folder

 
 